{"tid":220789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳 美 齡 遭 死 亡恐 嚇","createTime":"2017-04-28T08:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T08:29:16.000Z","uid":35370,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b8e8c4448c9f903398b711ee4128188ebe8d19","tid":220789,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"香港歌手陳美齡與日籍丈夫及三子現居東京，日前她遭網民死亡恐嚇，警方已插手調查。陳美齡近年關心社會，並擔任聯合國兒童基金大使及積極推行兒童色情法例，大前日竟有人在其twitter留言要大開殺戒：「如果唔承認兒童色情刊物，我會血洗陳美齡寓所！」當地傳媒亦大肆報道，指陳美齡赫見留言後由經理人報警，澀谷警署已着手跟進，更派警員到其豪宅附近巡邏。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20150922/19304316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20150922%2F19304316&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAde9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=51a12d3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20150922%2F19304316&h=4e2a3899\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20150922/19304316</a>"},{"pid":"66fc8802914b6cd881393279084f325d0254aea8","tid":220789,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2689b716ebc6f03498699f65ed49d317609ce01a","tid":220789,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:21:15.000Z","msg":"自作孽"},{"pid":"fd75e839345e3e56fcfc4bd879c9a642959e263b","tid":220789,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}